  ## Summary                                                                  
                                                                              
  Added a new EFO term **premenopausal** (EFO_0920060) to address issue #2652.
                                                                              
  **Term details:**                                                           
                                                                              
  • **ID**: EFO_0920060                                                       
  • **Label**: premenopausal                                                  
  • **Parent**: EFO:0001272 (adult) — sibling to EFO:0002721 (postmenopausal) 
  • **Definition**: "The reproductive years when a person has regular         
  menstrual periods, without experiencing any symptoms of perimenopause or    
  menopause."                                                                 
  • **Definition references**: PMID:40622713, PMID:41836154                   
  • **Cross-reference**: NCIt:C15491 ("Premenopausal")                        
  • **Synonyms**:                                                             
      • pre-menopausal (hasExactSynonym)                                      
      • pre-menopause (hasRelatedSynonym)                                     
      • premenopause (hasRelatedSynonym)                                      
  • **Issue tracker**: https://github.com/EBISPOT/efo/issues/2652             
                                                                              
